<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Meine Website mit Hintergrundbild</title>
    
    <!-- Favicon und App Icons -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="favicon.ico">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="android-chrome-icon" sizes="192x192" href="android-chrome-192x192.png">
    <link rel="android-chrome-icon" sizes="512x512" href="android-chrome-512x512.png">
    
    <!-- Web App Manifest -->
    <link rel="manifest" href="manifest.json">
    
    <!-- Theme Color für mobile Browser -->
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#2c3e50">
    <meta name="msapplication-TileColor" content="#2c3e50">
    
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            min-height: 100vh;
            
            /* Fallback-Hintergrund falls Bild nicht lädt */
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            
            /* Hintergrundbild Einstellungen */
            background-image: url('./Placeholder.bg.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-attachment: scroll; /* Fixed kann auf mobilen Geräten Probleme machen */
        }

        /* Overlay für bessere Lesbarkeit */
        .overlay {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        header {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 1rem 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        nav {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #3498db;
        }

        main {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3498db, #2980b9);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.4);
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.6);
        }

        footer {
            background-color: rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.9);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 2rem;
                margin: 1rem;
            }
            
            body {
                background-attachment: scroll;
            }
        }
        
        /* Debug-Styles für GitHub Pages */
        .debug-info {
            position: fixed;
            top: 10px;
            left: 10px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 12px;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: none;
        }
    </style>
    
    <script>
        // Debug-Script für GitHub Pages
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            console.log('Website geladen');
            console.log('URL:', window.location.href);
            
            // Überprüfe ob Hintergrundbild geladen wird
            const testImg = new Image();
            testImg.onload = function() {
                console.log('Hintergrundbild erfolgreich geladen');
            };
            testImg.onerror = function() {
                console.log('Hintergrundbild konnte nicht geladen werden');
                document.body.style.backgroundImage = 'none';
            };
            testImg.src = './Placeholder.bg.png';
        });
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="debug-info" id="debugInfo">
        Debug-Modus aktiviert
    </div>
    
    <div class="overlay">
        <header>
            <nav>
                <div class="logo">MeineLogo</div>
                <ul class="nav-links">
                    <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#about">Über uns</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact">Kontakt</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </header>

        <main>
            <div class="content">
                <h1>Willkommen auf meiner Website</h1>
                <p>Diese Website verwendet Ihr Hintergrundbild "Placeholder.bg.png". Das Bild wird als Vollbild-Hintergrund angezeigt und passt sich automatisch der Bildschirmgröße an.</p>
                <a href="#" class="cta-button">Mehr erfahren</a>
            </div>
        </main>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2025 Meine Website. Alle Rechte vorbehalten.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
